data.description: Beautiful Townhome in St Augustine! Downstairs, this lovely, townhome boasts an updated kitchen along with brand new flooring in the dining/living room combo. The backyard boasts a nice paved patio as well as an iron fenced in yard. The kitchen offers new appliances, quartz countertops and new backsplash. Upstairs, enjoy two spacious bedrooms and bathrooms as well as walk in closets for each. This gated neighborhood features a community pool with a club house, dog park nature trails, and is conveniently located near restaurants, shopping, I95 and top-rated St Johns County schools. The maintenance of the yard and exterior of the townhome is included in the monthly HOA fee. A new roof was completed in 2020. An attached one car garage is included.
